# The BNG-roundtrip SBML corpus is a regenerated artifact, not a
# tracked fixture: every *.xml is byte-derivable from
# models/bngl/ssa/*.bngl + BNG2.pl via run.py. load_check.json is the
# loader smoke-test report run.py writes alongside. Regenerate with:
#   cd bngsim && uv run python benchmarks/suites/sbml_roundtrip/run.py
*.xml
load_check.json
results/
__pycache__/
